Knife Fight - Season 1, Episode 7




Paderno vs. Santana

Los Angeles chefs Amar Santana and Mirko Paderno make a bet that leaves one of them up to his ears in potatoes and cooking with whole pig's head. Guests include: Elijah Wood, Krista Simmons and Beth Riesgraf.




Knife Fight - Season 1, Episode 8


Page vs. Trees

Chefs James Trees and Christian Page break down an entire goat. Guests: chefs Eric Greenspan and Octavio Becerra.




Original Air Date: 15-Oct-2013
